REPAINT MACRO
    MOVE.B #94, D0
    TRAP #15

    ENDM

CLRSCREEN MACRO
    MOVE.B #11, D0
    MOVE.W #$FF00, D1
    TRAP #15

    ENDM

UPDATE_KEY MACRO
    IFNE NARG-3
        FAIL ERROR UPDATE_KEY, ARGUMENTOS INSUFICIENTES
        MEXIT
    ENDC
    BTST.L \1, D1
    BNE SIK\@
    BCLR.B \2, \3
    BRA END\@
    SIK\@:
    BSET.B \2, \3
    END\@:

    ENDM